     <property name="text">
      <string>&lt;h3&gt;Orbital Volume Workflow&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Step 1 creates an entry plane (mesh) from a closed curve along the orbital rim. Step 2 segments the intraorbital volume from the CT using Fast Marching.&lt;/p&gt;</string>
     </property>
